OL,5,Cweather
OL,7,FSunday is likely to be the warmest day
OL,8,Fof the year so far, before
OL,9,Fthunderstorms and heavy rain put an
OL,10,Fend to a week of sunshine, the Met
OL,11,FOffice has said.
OL,13,FWhilst the hottest temperatures of the
OL,14,Fyear so far were recorded on Saturday,
OL,15,FSimon Partridge, a meteorologist at
OL,16,Fthe Met Office, said the records were
OL,17,F"not likely to last long" as
OL,18,Fforecasters expect it to be even
OL,19,Fwarmer on Sunday.
