OL,7,FThere are three yellow thunderstorm
OL,8,Fwarnings in place on Sunday.
OL,10,FOne covers most areas of the west of
OL,11,Fthe UK, including the majority of
OL,12,FWales, where thunderstorms are
OL,13,Fexpected between midday and 10pm.
OL,15,FThe second is for the western half of
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland between 11am and 7pm.
