OL,7,FThe third is for western parts of
OL,8,FScotland between 2pm on Sunday to 4am
OL,9,Fon Monday. Mr Partridge said this
OL,10,Fwarning is slightly different as more
OL,11,Fsignificant rainfall is expected.
OL,13,FPeople in areas with a yellow warning
OL,14,Fshould expect some disruption,
OL,15,Fespecially to travel.
OL,17,FSpray and sudden flooding could lead
OL,18,Fto difficult driving conditions and
OL,19,Fthere is a slight chance of power
OL,20,Fcuts, the Met Office said.
