OL,7,FOn Saturday, temperatures peaked at
OL,8,F25.9C in Herstmonceux, East Sussex,
OL,9,Fand in northern Scotland a temperature
OL,10,Fof 25.7C was recorded in Cassley.
OL,12,FGogerddan in Wales saw 25.1C, while
OL,13,Ftemperatures in Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fpeaked at 23.8C in Magilligan.
OL,16,FTemperatures climbed steadily over the
OL,17,Fweek, with the previous record set on
OL,18,FThursday, with a peak of 24.6C in
OL,19,FLondon's St James's Park.
