OL,7,FThe Royal Life Saving Society UK has
OL,8,Fwarned that warmer weather is directly
OL,9,Flinked to an increase in fatal
OL,10,Fdrowning incidents.
OL,12,FOn Friday, 17-year-old Ronalds Abele
OL,13,Fdied after getting into difficulty
OL,14,Fwhile swimming at the Embankment, in
OL,15,FWellingborough, and was pulled from
OL,16,Fthe water by emergency services,
OL,17,FNorthamptonshire Police said.
OL,19,FHe was pronounced dead in hospital.
